13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 4103, as
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 122, O.S.L. 2023 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 4103), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 4103. A. As used in this section:
18 1. “Degree-granting institution” means an institution that
19 offers education leading to an associate’s degree or higher;
20 2. “Non-degree-granting activity” means offering education or
21 training that does not lead to an associate’s degree or higher; and
22 3. “State authorization reciprocity agreement” means an
23 agreement among states, districts, and territories that establishes
